      "description": "A straightforward, budget-friendly vehicle for buyers who value affordability and utility. This car shows its age, but it remains a practical option for local driving, a first-time buyer, or someone needing inexpensive transportation without unnecessary extras. Offered with clear, honest positioning and priced to reflect strong value.",
