    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest budget-friendly car that starts, runs, and can still be a handy set of wheels for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but if you need affordable transportation, a project, or a parts car with some life left in it, this one is worth a look. Priced to sell and open to a reasonable conversation with serious buyers.",
