    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with plenty of life left for someone who wants simple, dependable transportation or a strong starter project. It shows cosmetic wear and age as expected, but the powertrain pulls well, starts up consistently, and the chassis feels composed for an older used car. A good candidate for a commuter, spare vehicle, or weekend tinkering, with straightforward mechanicals and real value for the money. Priced to move and worth a look if you want affordable wheels without the inflated price tag.",
