      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns errands into a story. It\u2019s an affordable set of wheels with plenty of personality, perfect for someone who appreciates a machine with grit, presence, and untapped potential. Whether you need a budget-friendly daily, a practical backup ride, or a project to make your own, this one offers a chance to get behind the wheel without breaking the bank. A little vision goes a long way here.",
