      "description": "Dependable transportation at an accessible price, this vehicle is a practical choice for anyone seeking honest value and everyday utility. It shows its age, but it remains a solid budget-minded option with plenty of life left for the right driver. A great fit for commuters, first-time buyers, or anyone looking for affordable wheels without unnecessary hype.",
