    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable option for someone who wants a budget-friendly daily, a first car, or a project to tinker with on the weekends. It has the kind of character you\u2019d expect at this price, and for the right buyer it could be a really handy little runaround. If you\u2019re after something inexpensive and straightforward, this one is well worth a look.",
